trans-unit.source: The NamedImagesCollection class represents a collection of <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.NamedImage> objects, which are objects that have an associated image and a name that is unique to the collection.
trans-unit.target: Klassen NamedImagesCollection representerer en samling av <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.NamedImage>objekter objekter som har en tilknyttet bildet og et navn som er unikt i samlingen.</xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.NamedImage>

trans-unit.source: This class is exposed as the <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.Chart.Images%2A> collection property of the root <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.Chart> object, and is only available at run time.
trans-unit.target: Denne klassen er eksponert som den <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.Chart.Images%2A>samlingen-egenskapen for rotmappen <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.Chart>objekt, og er bare tilgjengelig på kjøretidspunktet.</xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.Chart> </xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.Chart.Images%2A>

trans-unit.source: An image can be any object derived from the .NET Framework <xref:System.Drawing.Image> class, such as <xref:System.Drawing.Bitmap>, which is created dynamically.
trans-unit.target: Et bilde kan være et objekt som er avledet fra .NET Framework <xref:System.Drawing.Image>class, for eksempel <xref:System.Drawing.Bitmap>, som er opprettet dynamisk.</xref:System.Drawing.Bitmap> </xref:System.Drawing.Image>

trans-unit.source: The image can be stored in this collection, and then assigned at a later time to any image property in the <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.Chart> control, such as <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.Chart.BackImage%2A>.
trans-unit.target: Bildet kan lagres i denne samlingen og tilordnet en egenskap for bildet i <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.Chart>kontrollen, for eksempel <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.Chart.BackImage%2A>.</xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.Chart.BackImage%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.Chart> senere

trans-unit.source: When one of the image properties in the <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.Chart> control is set by specifying a `string` value, the <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.Chart.Images%2A> collection property, of type NamedImagesCollection, is first checked to see if an image with that name exists.
trans-unit.target: Når en av bildeegenskapene for i den <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.Chart>kontrollen er angitt ved å angi en `string` verdi, i <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.Chart.Images%2A>samlingen-egenskap av typen NamedImagesCollection, kontrolleres først for å se om det finnes et bilde med dette navnet.</xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.Chart.Images%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.Chart>

trans-unit.source: If a matching <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.NamedImage> object is found, this image is used.
trans-unit.target: Hvis en tilsvarende <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.NamedImage>objektet finnes, brukes dette bildet.</xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.NamedImage>

trans-unit.source: If a matching <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.NamedImage> object is not located, the string expression is treated as a URL, image resource name or pathname.
trans-unit.target: Hvis en tilsvarende <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.NamedImage>objektet finnes ikke, strengeuttrykk som skal behandles som en URL-adresse, ressurs Bildenavn eller banenavn.</xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.NamedImage>
